# Summary
This documentation explains how to configure Single Sign-On (SSO) integration between OneLogin and Amplitude for Scholarship, Growth, and Enterprise plan customers, detailing the step-by-step process of setting up the SAML 2.0 application in OneLogin and connecting it to Amplitude using metadata file exchange.

